# Dispatch Routing Configuration

Maps task intent → service endpoint for the Dispatch AI orchestrator. The config file lives at the repo root as `routing-config.yml`.

## Route Summary

| Route Key | Triggers | Service | Endpoint | Status |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| `ai_research` | research, summarize, explain, what is | PopeBot | `thepopebot-production-e881.up.railway.app` | ✅ Confirmed |
| `publication_writing` | write an article, draft a post, pitch, blog | Elite Writer | TBD | ⚠️ URL unknown |
| `ai_platform` | polsia, AI API, model endpoint | Polsia | `polsia-production.up.railway.app` | ✅ Confirmed |
| `task_management` | add task, create task, blocked | ClickUp MCP | `mcp://clickup` | ✅ Active |
| `knowledge_base` | add to KB, knowledge base, ingest | Nextra + Neon | `knowledge-base-nextra.vercel.app` | ⚠️ Unverified |
| `code_deploy` | push to github, deploy, fix the build | GitHub + Vercel | `mcp://github + mcp://vercel` | ✅ Active |
| `command_center` | dashboard, mission control, project status | Command Center | `command.insightprofit.live` | ✅ Active |
| `marketing_funnels` | funnel, checkout, GHL, order form | Go High Level | `mcp://ghl` | ✅ Active |
| `ecommerce` | shopify, family gift studio, FGS, POD | Family Gift Studio | TBD (Shopify URL) | ⚠️ TBD |
| `video_content` | video, vidrevamp, youtube, viral hook | VidRevamp | `vidrevamp.vercel.app` | ⚠️ Unverified |
| `aviation` | aviation, pilot, FAA, cargo, propel | Notion KB | `mcp://notion` | ✅ Active |
| `daily_briefing` | morning briefing, what\'s happening, daily brief | Chief of Staff | GitHub Actions dispatch | ✅ Active |

## Infrastructure

### Railway Services (Confirmed)

```
PopeBot:  https://thepopebot-production-e881.up.railway.app
Polsia:   https://polsia-production.up.railway.app
```

### Vercel Projects

```
knowledge-base-nextra  → https://knowledge-base-nextra.vercel.app
polsia-api             → https://polsia-api.vercel.app
vidrevamp              → https://vidrevamp.vercel.app (inferred)
elite-writer           → TBD (app confirmed, URL unknown)
```

### Custom Domains (Active)

```
command.insightprofit.live   → Command Center
supabase.insightprofit.live  → Self-hosted Supabase (Elite Writer backend)
```

