## Configuration File

The full annotated YAML config is at the repo root: [`routing-config.yml`](https://github.com/rtmendes/knowledge-base-nextra/blob/main/routing-config.yml)

To update routes, edit the YAML file directly and commit. The Dispatch orchestrator reads this file at startup.
